<plot>Explores the devotion of a man to his breakfast item of choice. Raised to only have one open box of cereal at any given time, Frank's curiosity is piqued by the cereal escapades of his best friend and cereal slut, Chuck. Frank falls victim to the temptation and it quickly becomes an addiction. His reckless actions result in a devastating confrontation and Frank must now live with the consequences of his decision.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?098348</url></doc>
